    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Back pain and thoracolumbar midline spinal tenderness to palpation\nSeatbelt sign: ecchymosis across the abdominal wall in the location of a lap belt\n[2]\nAbdominal pain\nLower extremity neurological deficits",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
